title: Valar Rereadis: TWOIAF - Before the Dragons
description:
Westeros 5-15 years prior to The Conquest. Featuring: Argilac the Arrogant, Queen Sharra and Ronnel Arryn, Harren the Black, Loren the Last, King Torrhen Stark, King Mern IX Gardener not to mention Aegon, Visenya, Rhaenys, their father Aerion and all their dragons... and a whole host of interconnected mini-stories.
